LA 311 Relative Hotspot Map (2025)

Shows where each complaint type is disproportionately concentrated relative to all other 311 calls. Darker = higher location quotient (local share ÷ citywide share).

A bright spot means this area has 3–10x the expected share of that type.
Areas with average or below-average shares are hidden.
Grid: ~200m cells • Min 5 requests/cell • Toggle layers at right
